    %% ============================================================================
    %% This diagram illustrates Snowflake's instant cloning feature using
    %% metadata pointers and copy-on-write semantics.
    %%
    %% Key Concepts:
    %% - Metadata-only operation (instant, regardless of data size)
    %% - Micro-partitions shared between original and clone
    %% - Copy-on-write: New partitions created only for modified data
    %% - Storage costs only for diverged data
    %% ============================================================================

