        MetaCopy["Metadata Copy Process:<br/>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br/>1. Copy metadata entry<br/>2. Point to same micro-partitions<br/>3. Update access control<br/>4. Return success<br/><br/>❌ NOT copied:<br/>- Actual data<br/>- Micro-partitions<br/>- File contents"]
    end

    OriMeta -.->|"Instant copy"| CloneSQL
    CloneSQL --> MetaCopy

