    end

    CloneMeta -.->|"User executes"| ModSQL
    ModSQL --> CopyOnWrite
    CopyOnWrite --> NewPartition

    %% Update pointer
    Ptr2 -.->|"BEFORE: Points to"| MP2
    Ptr2 -->|"AFTER: Points to"| NewPartition

